Title: One Year On
Plot: It's a big day for Mimi Maguire - it's her first wedding anniversary to Billy and they're going to renew their vows. Determined to make a fresh start, Mimi sets about throwing away memories of her past life with Paddy, but she alienates a furious Ruby with her comments about her dad.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence, sexual material, suicide & offensive language.
